Provides: install-btrfs
Depends: btrfs-progs, grml-debootstrap
Description: Prepare a new system for installing on btrfs, to use mkbackup-btrfs 
 Creates various btrfs-subvolumes on a newly created partition with btrfs and a /etc/fstab to mount all this subvolumes to install a new system with (grml-)debootstrap.
